Core Deliverables;
1. Fetch the stocks and render all of them into the page. (styling is provided)
2. Allow a user to buy a stock by clicking on it, when bought it should be added to MyPortfolio
3. Allow a user to sell a stock in their portfolio by clicking on the stock and it should be removed from their Porfolio
4. Allow a user to sort the list of stocks alphabetically by the ticker name as well as by ascending price
5. Allow a user to filter stocks based on the type of stock.